===Black Sabbath===
*Ozzy Osbournelead vocals, harmonica on &quot;The Wizard&quot;, tambourine
*Tony Iommiguitar
*Geezer Butlerbass
*Bill Warddrums

===Production===
*Rodger Bain production, Jew&#x27;s harp on &quot;Sleeping Village&quot;
*Tom Allom engineering
*Barry Sheffield engineering
*Marcus Keef graphic design, photography

