*Dave Cousins – voice on &quot;When the Walls Came Tumblin&#x27; Down&quot;

;Production
*(Colonel) Tom Allom – producer
*Louis &quot;Snook&quot; Austin – engineer
*Dick Plant – engineer
*Alan Schmidt – artwork

