* &quot;Perry Como Sings Merry Christmas Music&quot; (1946)
* &quot;A Sentimental Date With Perry&quot; (1949)
* &quot;TV Favorites&quot; (1952)
* &quot;Hits from Broadway Shows&quot; (1953)
* &quot;Around the Christmas Tree&quot; (1953)
* &quot;I Believe ~ Songs of All Faiths Sung by Perry Como&quot; (1953)
